snippet.title: Funny animals can always make you laugh and cheer you up - Funny animal compilation
snippet.description:
This is a very funny and cute animal compilation that will make you laugh for sure and make your day. Here you can see the best and funniest videos of cats, kittens, dogs, puppies, crabs, horses, frogs and so on. Which is your favourite animal clip? :P Hope you like our compilation, please share it and SUBSCRIBE! Watch also our other videos!

WANT TO SEE YOUR PET IN OUR COMPILATIONS?
Send your clips or links to: tigerlicensing@gmail.com

For more funny videos & pictures visit and like our Facebook page:
https://www.facebook.com/tigerstudiosfun
